    This class stores relation information to agile tools for a Timesheet Line.
    It will be used to look if there's a PPM Work plan that's integrated with the same entities, and automatically relate this timesheet line to the Project if it has timesheeting enabled.

    Matching will be done based on the LinkedTaskAgileEntityInfo info returned by the connector when mapping a task in the PPM work plan, so you need to ensure that the information returned is coherent if you want PPM to properly link to the timesheet line to the right Project or Task.
    A timesheet line will only match if the information in teh LinkedTaskAgileEntityInfo is as specific or less specific than the information returned in this class.
    For example, a timesheet line for Project 123 and Epic 456 will be linked to a project with a task mapped with Project 123, but not with a task mapped with Project 123/Epic 456/Feature 789.
    The connector instance must be the same between the work plan and the timesheet for automatic match to happen.
